    </StandardHierarchyLevel>
    <StatementCodes>
      <StatementCode>CCSS.ELA-Literacy.SL.11-12.4</StatementCode>
    </StatementCodes>
    <Statements>
      <Statement>Present information, findings, and supporting evidence, conveying a clear and distinct perspective, such that listeners can follow the line of reasoning, alternative or opposing perspectives are addressed, and the organization, development, substance, and style are appropriate to purpose, audience, and a range of formal and informal tasks.</Statement>
